rd-gewinner,8323513,ApplicationGallery.html|website=[[Jupiter Award (film award)|Jupiter-Filmpreis Online]]|accessdate=23 February 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[MTV Movie & TV Awards]]\n| [[MTV Movie Award for Best Performance|Best Performance in a Movie]]\n| rowspan=\"5\"|''[[Beauty and the Beast (2017 film)|Beauty and the Beast]]''\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2017/tv/news/mtv-movie-tv-awards-winners-list-1202410366/ |title=2017 MTV Movie and TV Awards: Complete Winners List |last=Knapp |first=JD |date=7 May 2017 |work=Variety |accessdate=8 May 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170508151541/http://variety.com/2017/tv/news/mtv-movie-tv-awards-winners-list-1202410366/ |archivedate=8 May 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[MTV Movie Award for Best Kiss|Best Kiss]] {{small|(shared with [[Dan Stevens]])}}\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"|[[Teen Choice Awards]]\n| [[Teen Choice Award for Choice Movie Actress \u2013 Sci-Fi/Fantasy|Choice Fantasy Movie Actress]]\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"4\"|<ref name=\"Winners\">{{cite web |last1=Ramos |first1=Dino-Ray |title=Teen Choice Awards 2017 Winners: 'Wonder Woman', 'Beauty And The Beast', 'Riverdale' Among Honorees |url=http://deadline.com/2017/08/teen-choice-awards-winners-2017-wonder-woman-beauty-and-the-beast-riverdale-fox-1202147975/ |website=Deadline Hollywood |publisher=enske Business Media, LLC. |date=13 August 2017 |accessdate=14 August 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| Choice Movie Ship {{small|(shared with Dan Stevens)}}\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Choice Liplock {{small|(shared with Dan Stevens)}}\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Choice Drama Movie Actress\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[The Circle (2017 film)|The Circle]]''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n! rowspan=\"5\"| 2018\n| [[Golden Raspberry Awards]]\n| [[Golden Raspberry Award for Worst Actress|Worst Actress]]\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite news |first=Christopher |last=Hooton |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/2018-razzie-awards-golden-raspberry-films-nomination-nominees-emma-watson-jennifer-lawrence-mother-a8171581.html |title=2018 Razzie awards: Emma Watson and Jennifer Lawrence among nominees for disservices to film |accessdate=5 February 2018 |newspaper=[[The Independent]] |date=22 January 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Empire Awards]]\n| [[Empire Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| rowspan=\"3\"|''Beauty and the Beast''\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/empire-film-awards-2018-the-last-jedi-leads-the-pack-with-nine-nominations-including-best-film-a3744171.html |title=Empire Film Awards 2018: The Last Jedi leads the pack with nine nominations including Best Actress for Daisy Ridley |first=Jennifer |last=Ruby |newspaper=[[London Evening Standard]] |date=19 January 2018 |accessdate=29 January 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Nickelodeon Kids' Choice Awards|Kids' Choice Awards]]\n| Favorite Movie Actress\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite web |first=Erik |last=Pedersen |url=http://deadline.com/2018/02/2018-kids-choice-awards-nominations-nickelodeon-stranger-things-dwayne-johnson-john-cena-1202303369/ |title=Nickelodeon Unveils 2018 Kids' Choice Awards Nominations |accessdate=3 March 2018 |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |date=26 February 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Saturn Awards]]\n| [[Saturn Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite web |first=Dave |last=McNary |url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/saturn-awards-nominations-2018-black-panther-walking-dead-1202727752/ |title='Black Panther,' 'Walking Dead' Rule Saturn Awards Nominations |accessdate=16 March 2018 |work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |date=15 March 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[People's Choice Awards]]\n| Style Star of 2018\n| {{n/a}}\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/2018/09/24/2018-peoples-choice-awards-nominees/1406792002/ |title=People's Choice Awards 2018: The nominees |author=USA TODAY Life staff |date=24 September 2018 |work=[[USA Today]]|access-date=6 October 2018 |language=en-US}}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"5\"| 2019\n| [[Washington D.C. Area Film Critics Association]]\n| [[Washington D.C. Area Film Critics Association Award for Best Ensemble|Best Ensemble]]\n| rowspan=\"12\"|''[[Little Women (2019 film)|Little Women]]''\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.wafca.com/awards/|title=The 2019 Washington DC Area Film Critics Association (WAFCA) Nominations|website=The Washington DC Area Film Critics Association|language=en|access-date=2019-12-09}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Boston Society of Film Critics]]\n| [[Boston Society of Film Critics Award for Best Cast|Best Ensemble Cast]]\n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://bostonfilmcritics.org/current-winners/|title=Current Winners \u2013 2019 Awards|website=[[Boston Society of Film Critics]]|language=en|access-date=2 January 2020}}</ref><br /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nextbestpicture.com/latest/the-2019-boston-society-of-film-critics-bsfc-winners|title=The 2019 Boston Society Of Film Critics (BSFC) Winners|website=Next Best Picture|language=en|access-date=2 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Florida Film Critics Circle]]\n| [[Florida Film Critics Circle Award for Best Cast|Best Ensemble]]\n| {{won}} \n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.floridafilmcritics.com/2019/12/19/marriage-story-leads-2019-florida-film-critics-awards-nominations/|title=Marriage Story leads 2019 Florida Film Critics Awards Nominations|website=Florida Film Critics Circle|language=en|access-date=2019-12-19}}</ref><br /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.floridafilmcritics.com/2019/12/23/2019-ffcc-winners/|title=Marriage Story and Portrait of a Lady on Fire tie for the most wins|website=Florida Film Critics Circle|language=en|access-date=2019-12-24}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Seattle Film Critics Society]]\n| Best Ensemble\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite web |url=http://seattlefilmcritics.com/2019/12/09/the-irishman-leads-the-2019-seattle-film-critics-society-nominations/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210112128/http://seattlefilmcritic